<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.3.1">
<l>karaiyeṭutta curicaṅkuṅ kaṉapavaḷat teḻukoṭiyum</l>
<l>tiraiyeṭuttu varupuṉalcūḻ tirukkaṇṇa purattuṟaiyum</l>
<l>viraiyeṭutta tuḻāyalaṅkal viṟalvaraittōḷ puṭaipeyara</l>
<l>varaiyeṭutta perumāṉuk kiḻantēṉeṉ varivaḷaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I lost my striped bangles to the lord who bore up a mountain</l>
<l>So that the scent-bearing tulasī garland shifted</l>
<l rend="indent">on his strong mountain[-like] shoulders,</l>
<l>[And] who dwells in Tirukkaṇṇapuram encircled by water where arrive,</l>
<l rend="indent">born on the waves,</l>
<l>Branches grown from thick coral and twisted conches which the shore bears.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
